 "name": "RPlog_Rise_of_the_Lizard_King",
 "title": "Rise of the Lizard King",
 "summary": "In the Spine Mountains of the Trandoshan world Dosha, near the village of Forak and the ruined temple of the New Sith Order once home to the nobleman Drayson Honos, the Lambda shuttle Emissary touches down in a hidden valley. Aboard, Lord Aldus Thel dons the mask, hood, and vocoder of Darth Venger as he and the Sith Warlord Korolov prepare for their roles, speaking of the service the Empire demands of all. Checking their weapons, the two Sith set out toward Forak, the scene heralding a dark ascent amid the ruins of the old order.",
